<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/style.css">
    <title>Bonafide Certificate</title>
    <style>
        /* A4 size styling */
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .container {
            width: 210mm;  /* A4 width */
            height: 297mm; /* A4 height */
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30mm 20mm; /* Adjust padding to look good on A4 size */
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        /* Header styling */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header img {
            width: 100px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .header h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .header p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Content section */
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: underline;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            margin-top: 100px;
        }

        .content span {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Footer section */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 260px;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer .signature {
            margin-top: 80px;
            margin-left: 700px;
        }

        /* Hide the button during print */
        @media print {
            body, .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
                border: none;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 25mm;
            }

            button {
                display: none; /* Hide button when printing */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <button onclick="window.print()">Download as PDF</button>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>CSMSS</h1>
            <h2>CHHATRAPATI SHAHU MAHARAJ SHIKSHAN SANSTHA'S</h2>
            <h2>CHH. SHAHU COLLEGE OF ENGINEERING</h2>
            <p>Approved by AICTE New Delhi, DTE (Govt. of Maharashtra) and affiliated to Dr. B.A.T.University, Lonere</p>
            <p>Kanchanwadi, Paithan Road, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar 431 002 (M.S)</p>
            <p>Ph. No.: (0240) 2379248, 2364663 Fax: (0240) 2370915</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:shahucce@gmail.com">shahucce@gmail.com</a> Website: <a href="http://www.csmssengg.org">www.csmssengg.org</a></p>
            <hr>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <span>Ref.: CSCOE/BONAFIDE/2024</span>
            <span style="margin-left: 360px;">Date: 04/09/2024</span>
            <h2>BONAFIDE CERTIFICATE</h2>
            <p>This is to certify that <strong><b><%= data.name %> </b></strong> is a bonafide student of this college studying in <strong><b> <%= data.class %>  <%= data.branch %> </b></strong> Engineering during the academic year 2024-2025. His date of birth as per college register is <%= data.Dob %>.</p>
            <p>His conduct and progress is satisfactory to the best of my knowledge. He bears a good moral character.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="signature">Principal</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    
</body>
</html>
